text: Aglaia rufinervis is a species of tree in the family Meliaceae. It is native to Thailand, Peninsular Malaysia, Singapore, Sumatra, Borneo and Java. ==References== rufinervis Category:Near threatened plants Category:Trees of Thailand Category:Trees of Malaya Category:Trees of Sumatra Category:Trees of Borneo Category:Trees of Java Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
